title: Oral Roberts vs. Ohio State - First Round NCAA tournament extended highlights
author: March Madness
description:
Oral Roberts shocked the world and took down Ohio State in OT. Kevin Obanor and Max Abmas scored 30 and 29 points for the Golden Eagles, respectively. Oral Roberts became just the 9th 15 seed ever to upset a 2 seed in NCAA tournament history, and the first since Middle Tennessee knocked off Michigan State in 2016. Watch the full extended highlights here.
